      "text": "2. Long term borrowing costs\n\nThese rates follow the 10-year Treasury yield.\n\nThis is not driven by the FFR, but rather by\nQE/QT and inflation expectations.\n\nIt affects mortgage rates & long term corporate\nbonds.",
      "fontSize": 25.908041961929555,
      "fontFamily": 5,
