      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Long term borrowing costs\n\nThese rates follow the 10-year Treasury yield.\n\nThis is not driven by the FFR, but rather by QE/QT and inflation expectations.\n\nIt affects mortgage rates & long term corporate bonds.",
