      "updated": 1776141543205,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. The search for yield / asset prices\n\nLow rates → investors pile into equities, real estate,\ncorporate bonds, private equity → asset prices rise\n\nWhen Treasuries are not offering a high enough\nreturn, investors are pushed to invest in other\nriskier assets.",
      "fontSize": 27.044075440304397,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. The search for yield / asset prices\n\nLow rates → investors pile into equities, real estate, corporate bonds, private equity → asset prices rise\n\nWhen Treasuries are not offering a high enough return, investors are pushed to invest in other riskier assets.",
